data.text:
Rathi is an Indian former actress, who appeared mostly in Tamil cinema and Telugu cinema.

Rathi Arumugam was born on September 23, 1982, in Bengaluru, Karnataka, India. Her birth geographical coordinates are 12° 58’ 19” North latitude and 77° 35’ 37” East longitude, with an altitude of 920 meters above sea level. Rathi Arumugam is currently 41 years old.

Astrologically, Rathi Arumugam falls under the Sun sign of Virgo, with Sagittarius as her Ascendant, Sagittarius as her Moon sign, and Capricorn as her Black Moon Lilith sign.
